<!-- ============ WHY OUR HISTORY WINS ============ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Decades of Retail DNA</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Experience you can't <span class="gradient-text">code.</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Shopify was born from e-commerce. NewStore and Sitoo are VC-backed startups. Teamwork Commerce is rooted in deep retail expertise — built by retail people, for retail people. That difference shows in every feature.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-building-store"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Retail-first founders</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Founded by Michael Mauerer, who spent decades building retail technology before launching Teamwork Commerce. We understand the Saturday afternoon rush because we've been there. This isn't a tech company learning retail — it's a retail company that mastered technology.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-brand-apple"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Native Apple partnership</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">We didn't just make an app. Our POS was co-designed with Apple's retail teams. While competitors use web technologies or Android, we are 100% native iOS — purpose-built for the speed, security, and aesthetic that enterprise brands demand.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-chart-line"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Private & profitable</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Many competitors are beholden to venture capital and its short-term pressures. Teamwork is founder-led and focused on long-term stability for our brands — not the next funding round. Your roadmap is driven by your needs, not investor exits.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-world"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Global from day one</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">While others are still figuring out international tax laws, we already support retailers in 40+ countries with native fiscal compliance baked into the platform. NF525, TSE, VAT, GST — it's not an afterthought, it's how we were built.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

